      • Parameter

        public Parameter(@Nullable
                 String name,
                 org.springframework.data.util.TypeInformation<T> type,
                 Annotation[] annotations,
                 @Nullable
                 PersistentEntity<T,P> entity)
        Creates a new PreferredConstructor.Parameter with the given name, TypeInformation as well as an array of Annotations. Will inspect the annotations for an Value annotation to lookup a key or an SpEL expression to be evaluated.
        参数:
        name - the name of the parameter, can be null
        type - must not be null
        annotations - must not be null but can be empty
        entity - must not be null.
